data.description: Welcome to 2 Beechcraft Rd, a charming ranch-style home located in a desirable neighborhood. This lovely home features 3 bedrooms and 1 full bath, making it perfect for a small family or individuals looking for a cozy space. With 864 square feet of living space, there's plenty of room to relax and unwind.Convenience is key in this home, as the laundry is located on the first floor for easy access. You'll also appreciate the proximity to the Wegmans shopping center, making grocery runs a breeze. Step outside and be greeted by a large fenced yard, offering privacy and security for your outdoor activities. The vinyl and laminate floorings throughout the home provide both durability and a modern aesthetic.Additionally, this home comes with a one-car garage, providing shelter for your vehicle and extra storage space.Don't miss out on the opportunity to make 2 Beechcraft Rd your new home. Schedule a viewing today and experience the comfort and convenience it has to offer.
